         <abstract><p>The <foreign xml:lang="gez">Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel</foreign> is a collection of 12 homilies in honour of <persName ref="PRS7049Michael"/>, one for each month.
            After the homilies, each monthly lecture contains a miracle, a comemmorative notice from the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2375Synaxa"/> and a <foreign xml:lang="gez">salām</foreign>
            to <persName ref="PRS7049Michael"/>. 
         The order and the absence of these texts change frequently.
         <listBibl type="secondary">
            <bibl><ptr target="bm:Lusini2005EAEDersanaM"/></bibl>
         </listBibl></p>
         </abstract>
